== 評價 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅27%，基於71條評論，平均分為4.3/10，觀眾評價卻高達62%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/underworld_awakening |title=''Underworld: Awakening'' |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]/{{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}} |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archive-date=2016-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028050607/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/underworld_awakening |dead-url=no }}</ref>；而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到39分，代表「普遍不佳」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/underworld-awakening |title=''Underworld: Awakening'' |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]/[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archive-date=2012-12-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ChMsy37b?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/underworld-awakening |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.4分，評價兩極，且多數好評皆傾向觀眾。

